dct_title_s: Carte de la Nle. Zelande visitée en 1769 et 1770 par le Lieutenant J. Cook Commandant de l'Endeavour, vaisseau de sa Majesté
dct_description_sm: "Tome III Pl. 7" from Hawkesworth's Relation des voyages ... Paris, Saillant et Nyon, 1774. Map of New Zealand showing track of Cook's Endeavour with relief shown by hachures, pictorially and by bathymetric soundings.
